---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Demo: Clínica Dental Premium | Tane Solutions" description="Ejemplo de Landing Page para Clínicas Dentales orientada a conversión." hideHeader={true}>
  
  <!-- Navigation / Back to Main -->
  <div class="fixed top-0 inset-x-0 z-50 p-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-3 pointer-events-none">
    <a href="/" class="pointer-events-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-200 text-slate-900 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-slate-100 transition-all shadow-lg">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
      Volver a Tane
    </a>
    <div class="pointer-events-auto px-4 py-1.5 bg-blue-500 text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20 rounded-full text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-center">
      Entorno Demo Clínico
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 font-sans selection:bg-blue-200">
    <!-- Hero Section (Clean & Trustworthy) -->
    <header class="relative pt-32 pb-24 px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
      <!-- Text Area -->
      <div class="flex-1 w-full relative z-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-sm font-bold mb-8">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          Financiación a medida disponible
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-[1.05]">
          Tu sonrisa es la <span class="text-blue-600">mejor carta de presentación.</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          Odontología avanzada sin dolor. Diagnosticamos tu caso y creamos un diseño digital de sonrisa en tu primera visita grauita.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <button class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl transition-all shadow-xl shadow-blue-600/30 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-lg hover:-translate-y-1">
            Reservar 1ª Visita Gratis
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <button class="bg-white hover:bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 transition-all flex items-center justify-center text-lg">
            Ver Tratamientos
          </button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">
          <div class="flex">
            {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-yellow-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>)}
          </div>
          <span class="ml-2">4.9/5 en Reseñas Reales</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Area with Graphic Elements -->
      <div class="flex-1 w-full lg:max-w-none relative z-10">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-square max-w-md mx-auto">
          <!-- Colorful organic blobs behind image -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-tr from-cyan-300 to-blue-500 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20 transform -translate-x-10 translate-y-10 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
          
          <img src="/images/dental_cover.png" alt="Clínica Dental Moderna" class="relative z-10 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl border-8 border-white" />
          
          <!-- Floating UI Element Left -->
          <div class="absolute -left-4 sm:-left-12 top-20 bg-white p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl z-20 flex items-center gap-4 animate-bounce" style="animation-duration: 3s">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600">
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="sm:w-6 sm:h-6"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-xs sm:text-base leading-tight">Clínica</p>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-[10px] sm:text-sm">Certificada</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Floating UI Element Right -->
          <div class="absolute -right-4 sm:-right-8 bottom-20 bg-white p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl z-20 flex items-center gap-3">
             <div class="flex -space-x-3">
               <img class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=1" alt="Doc">
               <img class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=2" alt="Doc">
               <img class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=3" alt="Doc">
             </div>
             <div class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm">
                <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">+5 Especialistas</p>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Services Grid -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white relative">
       <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-slate-200 to-transparent"></div>
       <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
         <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Tratamientos destacados</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Cubrimos todas las especialidades en el mismo centro para que no tengas que desplazarte a ninguna otra clínica.</p>
         </div>

         <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Service 1 -->
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow group">
               <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 20a8 8 0 1 0 0-16 8 8 0 0 0 0 16Z"/><path d="M12 14a2 2 0 1 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 0 0 4Z"/><path d="M12 2v2"/><path d="M12 20v2"/><path d="m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41"/><path d="m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41"/><path d="M2 12h2"/><path d="M20 12h2"/><path d="m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41"/><path d="m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41"/></svg>
               </div>
               <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Estética Dental</h3>
               <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Carillas de porcelana, blanqueamiento led y diseño digital de sonrisa para que brilles.</p>
               <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-2 transition-all">Saber más &rarr;</a>
            </div>
            <!-- Service 2 -->
            <div class="bg-blue-600 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl shadow-blue-600/20 text-white transform md:-translate-y-4">
               <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16h16V8l-6-6z"/><path d="M14 3v5h5M12 18v-6M9 15h6"/></svg>
               </div>
               <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Implantología Avanzada</h3>
               <p class="text-blue-100 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Recupera la funcionalidad de tu boca en 24h con implantes de titanio de carga inmediata.</p>
               <a href="#" class="text-white font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-2 transition-all">Saber más &rarr;</a>
            </div>
            <!-- Service 3 -->
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow group">
               <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><line x1="3.27" y1="6.96" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="20.73" y1="6.96" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
               </div>
               <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Ortodoncia Invisible</h3>
               <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Alineadores transparentes y cómodos. Corrige tus dientes sin que nadie note que llevas aparato.</p>
               <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-2 transition-all">Saber más &rarr;</a>
            </div>
         </div>
       </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 text-white">
      <div class="absolute inset-0">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588776814546-1ffcf47267a5?q=80&w=2000&auto=format&fit=crop" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20" alt="Consultorio dental" />
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
         <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Ven a conocernos. <br/>La primera consulta incluye escáner 3D.</h2>
         <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Vuelve a sonreír, comer y hablar con total seguridad. Estamos en el centro de tu ciudad.</p>
         <button class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-400 text-white font-bold px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl transition-transform hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl">
            Llamar ahora: 900 123 456
         </button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
